data.description: Welcome to your 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath sanctuary on a charming corner lot, offering 2,276 square feet of pure elegance and comfort. Step inside this exquisite abode and discover an open-concept masterpiece. The heart of the home is the spacious center island kitchen, a culinary haven that boasts ample cabinet space, stunning granite countertops, under-cabinet lighting, and a convenient breakfast bar. With seamless connectivity to the family room, your gatherings here are bound to be memorable, centered around the captivating corner fireplace. Natural light floods every nook, accentuating the tile plank flooring throughout. For privacy, the bedrooms are thoughtfully arranged in a split plan, with plush carpeting in all the right places.The master suite is a retreat unto itself, with enough room for a king-sized bed. Double doors lead to a spa-inspired master bath featuring double vanities, a separate tub, and a shower to give you that cherished spa feel. And there's more – a spacious master walk-in closet that conveniently connects to the laundry room for the owner's ultimate convenience. All secondary bedrooms are generously sized, bathed in natural light, and offer ample closet space, ensuring everyone's contentment. Outdoor living is equally enchanting. A covered front porch beckons you to unwind, while the extended patio is destined to become your BBQ paradise. Notably, this home boasts its own guest-friendly half bath, adding a touch of luxury to your entertaining. But the surprises don't end there. With a 2-car extended garage, this home offers ample space for your personal pursuits – whether you dream of a workshop, home gym, or any other creative venture. Convenience is key, with this home located just 12 minutes from FT Cavazos, a mere 17 minutes from Killeen airport, and in close proximity to retail stores in Killeen and Harker Heights. This is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade waiting for you. Loan Assumption is available.CALL NOW FOR A SHOWING!
